        <p class="project-title">Vintour</p>
        <p>
          Built using <strong>Python, Django, and Postgres</strong>, Vintour is a tour planning service for Napa and Sonoma that won't try to sell the user on a service.
          I scraped all winery data to JSON for over 1,000 wineries and then seeded our Postgres database, forming the core of Vintour’s functionality.
          This being a team project, I learned plenty about GitHub workflow and common versioning issues. I also had to learn web scraping in a hurry, and got to work out my SQL and Django query muscles.
          <a href="https://vintour.herokuapp.com" target="_blank"><button>Check it out!</button></a>
